                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130714-13-off73 t18130714-13-cd70"></join>, feloniously did dispose of, and put away a certain forged order for the payment of 500 l. with intention to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130714-13-victim174" type="victimName">
