               they, before the said felonies were committed, to wit, on the <rs id="t18130714-13-cd74" type="crimeDate">18th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130714-13-off69 t18130714-13-cd74"></join>
